          "description": "I've been coming here for years. The office changed staff many many times. I've never had a billing problem, ever. I've recommended them to my coworkers. Most of them loved it until they almost got scammed. I was soooo embarrassed hearing all their billing issues and inconsistent pricing when I was the one that told them to go there. Smh.\nI have excellent coverage. I was told I need a big surgery.and my insurance won't cover it. Lies. I called my insurance after I left the office. Both procedures are covered 60-80%. I called back. They said the billing person was out for 2 days. They called me the next day and said im not covered. They wouldnt tell me who they spoke to at my insurance company. Of course, because they didn't even call them! My insurance rep  didn't even see any claims from that office. Something fishy is going on. I found a new dental specialist and my procedures ARE covered. If you do not have insurance, this is the place for you. They want out of pocket money real bad. No claims. No insurance. Do your research before you proceed. Used to love this place. Very disappointed.",
