        {
          "username": "Merna Rezk",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "107035748572365442479",
          "user_review_count": 121,
          "user_photo_count": 184,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVW9hDh7hOW1xOTjc79oja9YtR5kIHM0z3FOqidOSxQWHqZCTvs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Not sure how this place gets 4.7 star reviews but my whole experience was horrible. Went for a hygienist and its the first time i ever went for teeth cleaning and it was only one person. She left the suction hanging in my mouth and it kept sucking my cheeks inside i flinched many times, completely ignored, and the suction got stuck in my cheeks inside and bruised me!! And after a while the hygienist was like oh i see what you mean it pinched you. And the cleaning was not the best!!! My teeth still felt sandy from the inside and she didnt even floss??? Never been a dentist that doesnt floss your teeth on your hygienist appointment. Yes she was nice and taught me some techniques.\n\nEvery dentist i have been to, always two people working, this clinic is just all about saving money.\n\nThen i got an orthodontist consultation and he was soooo pushy on removIng ALL wisdom tooth in one sitting.\n\nI tried to voice my concerns and the dentist was not even hearing what I am saying only pushing one agenda!! I have never seen a doctor push one agenda on a patient and my case is not emergent that I had to take all four out. He literally went to the front desk and said ok book her for wisdom tooth removal although i explicitly said let me think about it.\n\nFor sure this place number one care is milking money and not actually listening or caring for the patient.\n\nFor sure switching dentists. First and last time",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0M1pFVTNURVUyYlZkaFQzTm9ZV052TVhKalkyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x1d9f26a6aa6358a8!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkt3ZEU3TEU2bVdhT3NoYWNvMXJjY2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "2 months ago",
