        {
          "username": "Ryan Peffers",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "105253660177783998286",
          "user_review_count": 27,
          "user_photo_count": 6,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX58FPY89c_WiyatqPxwmiMnpRAJc1xplBjU0KpTCM9uPkyYrZnsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "So generally, the hygeniest and dentists have been good here.\nThis is a PE owned dental office and I have rarely been seen by the same dentist twice. There seems to be a revolving door here.\nI have a problem with the front office communication both around benefits and costs of procedures. They have never accurately read my insurance to understand I am covered for 4 cleanings a year.\nLikewise they failed to notify me that my new insurance was out of network until after I got a standard filling and it ended up being almost triple what I would have paid for an in network filling.\nWhen I brought this up to them, the front office's apathy towards this missed communication left me very disappointed in the whole experience. I won't be going back (given I also just found out I am out of network on my last appointment) and would recommend people check their insurance/rely on their own research rather than trust the front office to notify you of what your benefits cover.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNMlZFYzJXakJPUlZJMVMwdFpYMWt5VjJSek1uYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x1d9f26a6aa6358a8!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkM2VEc2WjBORVI1S0tZX1kyV2RzMnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-04-28T21:12:45+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Tsi P",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "105808093476968253920",
          "user_review_count": 6,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMWkbnkPtRn6DAgRMXt4LQwxJvxkIrFGusR2MEs83b25z4rg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I want to start by saying that I am petrified of the dentist- I get the worst anxiety whenever I have to go. That being said, I recently needed a root canal and was so nervous about the whole experience.\n\nThe entire team at this office is incredible. From the receptionist and financial department to the assistants and dentists, everyone is fantastic. Dr. Chang and Genesis performed my root canal, and I have nothing but amazing things to say. I didn\u2019t feel anything, they checked in on me frequently, and most importantly they helped calm my nerves and made me feel comfortable the entire time.\n\nMy actual dentist, Dr. Vimo, is the best! She\u2019s so sweet, honest, patient, and incredibly helpful. I honestly love her. As someone who usually hates going to the dentist, they\u2019ve completely changed the experience for me and made every visit feel easy and comfortable. I cant recommend them enough!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CcU9YcElhVTVJTUZoT1ZEQnpOMDVRUWpNeGQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x1d9f26a6aa6358a8!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnBqOXpIaU5IMFhOVDBzN05QQjMxd3c%7C%7C?hl=en",
